<HEAD1>gruk</HEAD1>
@{<E>Peter Hein</E>@} nAme ekjan kabi Achhen, tini chhTochhoTo
kabitA lekhen (anekTA rabi ThAkurer lekhan bA sfulinger
mata). kabitAguloke tini balen gruk. tAr madhye ekTA eirakam--
<P/>
@{<E>
The way to success?<BR/>
Well, it is plain,<BR/>
And simple to express:<BR/>
Err, and err, and err again<BR/>
But less and less and less!
</E>@} 
ekTA anubAd eirakam karechhi--
<PRE>
buddhi kholAr mantarTA 
balei feli  man tore-
bhuler pare bhul kare yA,
ekTu ekTu kam kare. 
</PRE>
</NOTE>

